# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:15
translate portuguese izzys6_fad01e22:

    # gl "Yeah, I mean everybody has family right?"
    gl "Sim, quer dizer, toda a gente tem família, certo?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:17
translate portuguese izzys6_dacc2484:

    # gl "My mom's in jail, but we still keep in contact."
    gl "A minha mãe está na prisão, mas ainda mantemos contacto."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:18
translate portuguese izzys6_e1adb706:

    # gl "My auntie comes around and helps a lot. We're pretty close."
    gl "A minha tia vem visitar-me e ajuda-me imenso. Somos muito próximas."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:19
translate portuguese izzys6_56258dac:

    # gl "Then I have my two little brothers, who are just about the only people I really care about in this world."
    gl "Depois tenho os meus dois irmãos mais novos, que são praticamente as únicas pessoas de quem realmente gosto neste mundo."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:20
translate portuguese izzys6_4e06d3eb:

    # pc "How old are they?"
    pc "Que idade têm eles?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:22
translate portuguese izzys6_f88bb2e6:

    # gl "Eight and ten. They're little shits too. Always getting into trouble."
    gl "Oito e dez anos. Também são uns pestinhas. Estão sempre a meter-se em sarilhos."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:23
translate portuguese izzys6_ec1932e4:

    # gl "But I love the hell out of them."
    gl "Mas adoro-os de morte."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:24
translate portuguese izzys6_b38aac72:

    # pc "You live with your aunt?"
    pc "Vives com a tua tia?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:26
translate portuguese izzys6_9972240b:

    # gl "No, I have my own place. My brothers live with me."
    gl "Não, tenho a minha própria casa. Os meus irmãos vivem comigo."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:27
translate portuguese izzys6_72975c50:

    # pc "That must be tough. Taking care of your brothers while also trying to live your own life."
    pc "Isso deve ser difícil. Cuidar dos teus irmãos enquanto tentas viver a tua própria vida."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:28
translate portuguese izzys6_28120250:

    # gl "Yeah. Been doing it since I was sixteen though."
    gl "Sim. Mas faço isso desde os dezasseis anos."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:29
translate portuguese izzys6_75c9650c:

    # pc "Who looks after them while you're out at the park?"
    pc "Quem cuida deles enquanto estás no parque?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:30
translate portuguese izzys6_6e1d3f7f:

    # gl "Nobody. They're all right. They just go to sleep anyway."
    gl "Ninguém. Eles ficam bem. Acabam por adormecer de qualquer maneira."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:31
translate portuguese izzys6_cc0c29d6:

    # gl "Besides, Paul is ten. He's okay for a little while by himself."
    gl "Além disso, o Paul tem dez anos. Ele fica bem sozinho por um bocadinho."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:32
translate portuguese izzys6_e04e660c:

    # pc "I guess so. Just seems like a hard childhood."
    pc "Acho que sim. Só que parece uma infância difícil."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:34
translate portuguese izzys6_69333f16:

    # gl "Don't go judging my life, Twig."
    gl "Não julgues a minha vida, Twig."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:35
translate portuguese izzys6_4e440deb:

    # gl "We don't have much, but we're doing fine."
    gl "Não temos muito, mas estamos bem."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:36
translate portuguese izzys6_dc16f2c8:

    # pc "You're right, sorry."
    pc "Tens razão, desculpa."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:38
translate portuguese izzys6_2e9e70e6:

    # gl "It's okay."
    gl "Não faz mal."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:39
translate portuguese izzys6_ea66dd1b:

    # gl "Just don't worry. I'll take care of my brothers."
    gl "Não te preocupes. Eu cuido dos meus irmãos."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzys6.rpy:40
translate portuguese izzys6_6833e9a1:

    # gl "Always have. Always will."
    gl "Sempre cuidei. Sempre cuidarei."

